h1= title
div(ng-controller='ResumeListController')
  #main-container
    #main.wrapper.clearfix
      article
        header
          div(x-ng-repeat="resume in resumes")
            .tile
              h2 {{resume.industry}}
              p {{resume.description}} 
              p {{resume.resumeText}} 
              p {{resume.date}}
              a(href="#/resumes/{{resume._id}}") Show
      
      aside
        h3 Look at and comment on resumes
        p
          | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Aliquam sodales urna non odio egestas tempor. Nunc vel vehicula ante. Etiam bibendum iaculis libero, eget molestie nisl pharetra in. In semper consequat est, eu porta velit mollis nec. Curabitur posuere enim eget turpis feugiat tempor. Etiam ullamcorper lorem dapibus velit suscipit ultrices.

  if user
    form.pure-form.pure-form-aligned(ng-submit='newResume()')
      fieldset
        .pure-control-group
          label(for='POST-industry') Industry:
          input#POST-industry(type='text', ng-model='industry') 
        .pure-control-group
          label(for='POST-description') Description:
          input#POST-description(type='text', ng-model='description')
        .pure-control-group
          label(for='POST-resumeText') resumeText:
          input#POST-resumeText(type='text', ng-model='resumeText')
        .pure-controls
          button.pure-button.pure-button-primary(type='submit') Save Resume